Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://yahoofinancer.rsquaredacademy.com/, https://github.com/rsquaredacademy/yahoofinancer
BugReports: https://github.com/rsquaredacademy/yahoofinancer/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
